title: Empire of the Dark [1990 - USA] science fiction
description:
Empire of the Dark (1990 - USA)

Science Fiction
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0099498/


Policeman Richard Flynn entered another dimension twenty years ago to rescue the woman that he loved and her infant child who was slated to be sacrificed by an evil cult. Today, the baby is a young man who is again being sought after by the same cult in order for them to add his life to a cycle that will leave the earth vulnerable to ancient demons and ghouls. Richard Flynn and the young man join forces and embark on a crazy trip to find and destroy the cult. Their adventure virtually takes them to hell and back.
